  <brief_title>L-asparaginase Monotherapy as Salvage Treatment in Patients With NK/T Cell Lymphoma</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of L-asparaginase Monotherapy as Salvage Treatment in Patients With NK/T Cell Lymphoma</official_title>
  <sponsors>
